Dialogs.Dialog: By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What kinds of TV shows do you usually watch, ▲小早川＊▲？
...Why？
Um... Somehow, I just want to know.
Somehow, you just want to know？
Yeah.
Somehow, I just don't want to tell you.
(She just copied my words.)
I just copied your words. Is there a problem？
(Does she have ESP！？)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What kind of food do you like？ Or, do you have anything you dislike？
Just normal food. Are you expecting something out of the ordinary？ If so, I'm sorry.
No, normal food is fine. Well, you like sweets, don't you？
Hmm, I don't hate sweets, but I prefer potato chips. I can eat them instead of my meals. It has to be the ones from Kalbee, though.
Why？ I think the ones from Lei's are good too. I favor especially the sour cream flavor.
That was before. After Kalbee released the seaweed and salt flavor, I always go for Kalbee.
Hmm...？ Is that so？
That is so. Ah... now I'm craving them... I'm gonna buy some on the way home▼
(You really love potato chips, huh？ I think this is beyond normal...)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
I think I should ask you this question. Do you play any sports, ▲小早川＊▲？
Not at all. And I think I should give you this answer.
I guess so. That's what I thought.
...What did you think？
Because your arms and legs look so flimsy, I don't think you would enjoy playing sports.
Don't look at me with such a weird face. ...At least I have a sport I'm good at.
Really？ What is it？
Martial arts.
...Light kick！ Hiya！
Ouch！ Did you learn this from fighting games！？
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What kind of music do you usually listen to？
Nice question.
Really？
Yeah, you'll understand me more if you understand the music I'm listening to.
I see. Then what genre do you listen to？
I don't care much about genre or artists. I'm quite into the Second British Invasion.
British... what？
The sounds are much poorer than today's music, as they were made for mass selling, but some of them are very good...
T-That sounds difficult...
No！ They are so easy to listen to. Geez, were you listening？ Like, if we talk about the current Visual Kei...
(I feel like I just stepped on a land mine...)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
Do you have any interest？ ...Ah, I mean besides music.
Besides music？ ...Why？
You might be interested in something else, but I just can't picture you interest in anything besides music, ▲小早川＊▲.
Why？ I have interest in stuff other than music.
Really？ Such as...？
(You don't have any, huh？)
Men.
What！？ ...You're kidding, right？
I'm not kidding. Lately, I'm having fun fooling around with them.
W-Wait a minute. That's very dangerous and you're a girl...
Dangerous？ Why？
Why...？ Think about your age. You're not a kid anymore. You know what I'm trying to say, right？
Rinko is still a kid, so she doesn't understand！ Hey, hey. Why is it dangerous？
(...Huh？ Eh？)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What's your favorite animal ▲小早川＊▲？
Animal？ Well... This is complicated. Most of them kind of stink.
Well, they're animals... Hmm, how about cats...？
Cats！？ Are there cats here？ Where？
Eh？ I was about to say that you look like someone who would like cats...
What？ Of course, I like cats！
Of course...？ But cats are animals, too, right？
No！ Cats are... Well, how can I put this...？ They are just different. Ah~！ I want to have cats▼
Cats always cry "nya" with low voices, right？ And, and they usually curl up like a ball...
(Then your favorite animal is a cat or many cats, ▲小早川＊▲...)
By the way...
Rinko
Hmm？
I might have asked you this before, but do you have any dream for your future, ▲小早川＊▲？
Dream, huh...？ A dream for Rinko is not such a big deal.
I see... You don't care much about it then.
It's just too ridiculous.
I'm not going to laugh.
Then if I tell you, you must tell me your dream.
Okay.
I want to write books.
Really？ I see. You really love reading books, ▲小早川＊▲.
I just want to write easy reading books for little kids. Something that will be put on children's bookshelves.
Like something for summer reading list？
Yeah！ In summer, a lot of kids will be reading my books. Those kids will be impressed with what I wrote.
Ahaha！ That sounds great. What I'd expect from you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Really？ Hehe...
Hey, and now, how about your dream？
Eh？ My dream... is to make you happy. Yeah, that's it, ▲小早川＊▲.
Geez！ A crafty answer！
(Yup, but I'm sure you can write nice books, ▲小早川＊▲.)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What is your dream for the future, do you have plans, ▲小早川＊▲？
Like what I want to be in the future？
Yeah, what is it...？
When people are at a certain age, they'll start talking about this, huh？
Urgh... But, at least you should've already thought about it, right？
No. No future for me. Look at how the Earth is deteriorating now.
You mean the global warming or starvation problems？ But we're working on these issues, so it might be okay...
Then how about the aliens？ They will invade the Earth, right？
A-Aliens？ ▲小早川＊▲...
Well, I think we'll be okay for a while...
Yeah. Alien invasion, huh？ That must be a big problem, right？
Enough. Shut up！
By the way...
Rinko
Yeah？
Even you have a female role model, right ▲小早川＊▲？
You mean I should have one？ But... I can't think of any.
Hmm... I see.
Women usually mature faster than men. That's such a disadvantage.
Really？ But I think men also have their own disadvantages.
I didn't mean it that way.
I feel like I'll turn into a woman soon and I might not be myself like I used to be anymore...
Hmm... Are we talking about physical education now...？
Geez！ Shut up！ Get away from me！
(What is this...？)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
Even you have a female role model, right ▲小早川＊▲？
"Even me," you said？
Must be your imagination. Well, do you have any？
None.
(As I thought.)
Female, huh？ Women are only ever recognized as supporting roles.
People only mention us as "that guy's wife" or "that female writer" or something like that.
Yeah, that's true.
Rinko doesn't want to be like that. What Rinko wants is different.
Different...？ You mean you want a male role model？
No！ What Rinko wants is to be different... Well... Someone like you will never understand！
(You don't even understand it yourself, I think.)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
Even you have a female role model, right ▲小早川＊▲？
Role model？ Hmm...
I don't know if this counts as a role model but I respect women who become mothers.
Mothers？
Think of a mother who carries her child wherever she goes and has to spend time with the kid all day. Rinko can't do that.
That's really amazing... But I think when you become a mother, you'll be able to do that, too, ▲小早川＊▲.
When Rinko becomes a mother...？
Yeah. And one day, I'll also become a father...
Yeah, Papa▼
Just practice.
(T-This is very, very embarrassing...)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
What kinds of movies do you like ▲小早川＊▲？
Movies？ Movies, huh？ Hah...
Oh, you don't like to watch movies then.
The plots always involve incurable illnesses or mankind's crises. Just look at the posters and I can tell the whole story.
You can tell, huh？ Well, how about comedy or horror movies ▲小早川＊▲？
Those movies only force me to laugh or make me scared. I think that's tiring.
Well, movie producers have to put lots of effort in making them...
Why can't we have movies with no one dying, stupid humor, and no ghosts？ Just something about a peaceful world.
I'm sure there are some like that... But will you want to watch them？
Well... Let's stop this discussion.
(What will satisfy her then...？)
By the way...
Rinko
Yes？
You really like reading, right ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, pretty much.
Do you have books you like in particular？
Some American novels from the 1950's and 1960's. You won't understand even if I tell you.
Oh, don't underestimate me.
No, I'm not. People around my age just don't read the books that I like...
And these books are not something everyone can understand.
You really think I won't understand？
I don't know if I want you to understand or not... I really don't know.
